<h1>How do I buy crypto?</h1>
<p>Choose a cryptocurrency exchange or a brokerage platform.
  Create an account and complete the verification process.
  Link your bank account or payment method to the exchange.
  Choose the cryptocurrency you want to buy.
  Enter the desired amount and review the transaction details.
  Confirm the purchase and wait for the transaction to be completed.
  The purchased crypto will be credited to your exchange account.
  You can then manage, trade, or transfer your crypto as desired.
  Remember to consider factors like security, fees, and user experience when selecting an exchange.
  Always store your crypto in a secure wallet to keep it safe.</p>
